-- U.K. BBA July Mortgage Approvals Rise 9.6% from June to 28,441
-- B y   J e n n i f e r   R y a n
-- 2012-08-23T08:30:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-23/u-k-bba-july-mortgage-approvals-rise-9-6-from-june-to-28-441.html
U.K. mortgage approvals rose 9.6
percent in July from the previous month to 28,441, the  British
Bankers Association  said in an e-mailed statement today.
Approvals are down from 34,125 a year earlier.  To contact the reporter on this story:
